data.description: House Hacking: Located just half a block up from downtown, this duplex is perfectly situated within  walking distance to all your favorite restaurants, shopping spots, and grocery store! But wait, it gets even better! This property offers an incredible opportunity  for house hacking! Imagine living in one apartment and renting out the other, allowing you to save big on your mortgage. Priced to sell, this duplex is not only a fantastic place to call home but also an excellent investment opportunity. Don't miss out on the chance to make your money work for you.
